snippet.title: Deadlink - Interport Major Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1676130/Deadlink/ 
Fight the new Interport Corporation in the newest Deadlink update!

Get ready to put a sizable dent in the profits of megacorporations in Deadlink, a guns-blazing cyberpunk FPS with roguelite elements. Your mission is to conduct covert ops while piloting a humanoid combat shell. And no, "covert" doesn’t mean "quiet."

See more Deadlink content: 
https://youtu.be/L5SLJpdcfLU 
https://youtu.be/glok5ozuIIE
https://youtu.be/g9zVnmjlG_w

#deadlinkgame #fps #cyberpunk
